<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - BLKND</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif; }
        .page-header { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 80px 0 40px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .team-member { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .team-member img { width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .stats-section { background-color: #212529; color: #fff; padding: 60px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-nav text-white" style="background-color: #212529; padding: 10px 0; font-size: 14px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                <div>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px;"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px;"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px;"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                </div>
                <div><span>Free shipping on orders over $50</span></div>
                <% if(!user){ %>
                    <div>
                        <a href="/login" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px;">Login</a>
                        <a href="/signup" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 15px;">Register</a>
                    </div>
                <% } else {%>
                    <div>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 0rem;"><%= user.name %></p>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white sticky-top" style="padding: 20px 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/index" style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700;">BLKND</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/index">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/shop">Shop</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="nav-icons d-flex align-items-center">
                    <a href="#" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#searchModal" style="color: #212529; font-size: 18px; margin-left: 20px;"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></a>
                    <a href="/profile" style="color: #212529; font-size: 18px; margin-left: 20px;"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></a>
                    <a href="/wishlist" style="color: #212529; font-size: 18px; margin-left: 20px;"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></a>
                    <a href="/cart" style="color: #212529; font-size: 18px; margin-left: 20px; position: relative;">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        <span style="position: absolute; top: -8px; right: -8px; background: #212529; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; padding: 2px 6px; font-size: 10px;">0</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="modal fade" id="searchModal" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close float-end" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <input type="search" class="form-control form-control-lg" placeholder="Search products...">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="mb-2">About Us</h1>
            <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                <ol class="breadcrumb">
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/index">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="breadcrumb-item active">About</li>
                </ol>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mb-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Our Story</h2>
                <p>Founded in 2020, BLKND has become a leading destination for fashion enthusiasts seeking quality, style, and affordability. What started as a small boutique has grown into a trusted online fashion retailer serving customers worldwide.</p>
                <p>We believe that fashion should be accessible to everyone, which is why we carefully curate our collections to offer the latest trends at prices that won't break the bank. Our commitment to quality ensures that every piece in our store meets the highest standards.</p>
                <p>At BLKND, we're more than just a fashion store â€“ we're a community of style lovers who believe in expressing individuality through clothing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441986300917-64674bd600d8?w=600" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Store">
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row align-items-center mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>Our mission is to empower individuals to express themselves through fashion. We strive to provide a seamless shopping experience, exceptional customer service, and a diverse range of products that cater to every style and occasion.</p>
                <p>We are committed to sustainable fashion practices and work closely with our suppliers to ensure ethical production methods. Your satisfaction is our priority, and we're here to make your shopping experience extraordinary.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556228578-0d85b1a4d571?w=600" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="Mission">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-section">
        <div class="container">
